\c 28
\s Dhavhidhi anonyengetera kuti arwirwe naJehovha
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndichadana kwamuri, Jehovha; dombo rangu, regai kundinyararira; zvimwe, kana mukandinyararira, ndingafanana navanoburukira kugomba.
\v 2 Inzwai inzwi remikumbiro yangu, kana ndichichema kwamuri, kana ndichisimudzira maoko angu kunzvimbo yomukati yeimba yenyu tsvene.
\v 3 Musandibvuta pamwe chete navakaipa, navanoita zvakashata; ivo vanotaura rugare kuna vavanogara navo, asi zvakashata zviri mumoyo mavo.
\v 4 Muvape zvakaenzana nebasa ravo, uye zvakaenzana nezvakaipa zvavakaita, muvape zvakaenzana nokubata kwamaoko avo; muvaitire sezvakavafanira.
\v 5 Zvavasina kurangarira mabasa aJehovha, nezvaakabata namaoko ake, iye achavaputsa, akasavavakazve.
\p
\v 6 Jehovha ngaavongwe, nokuti akanzwa inzwi rokukumbira kwangu.
\v 7 Jehovha ndiye simba rangu nenhovo yangu; moyo wangu wakavimba naye, ndikabatsirwa; saka moyo wangu unofara kwazvo, ndichamurumbidza norwiyo rwangu.
\v 8 Jehovha ndiye simba ravo, ndiye nhare yokuponesa kumuzodziwa wake.
\v 9 Ponesai vanhu venyu, muropafadze nhaka yenyu; muvafudzewo, muvatakure nokusingaperi.
